ui
Class UIController

java.lang.Object
  ui.UIController
Direct Known Subclasses:
CommandLineUIController, GUIController
public abstract class UIController
extends java.lang.Object

This class handles the communication between control units (in control.*) and the user interface. This class uses the GoF design pattern Singleton.
